    {
      "$type": "Models.Factorial.Experiment, Models",
      "DisabledSimNames": null,
      "Name": "SimulationExp",
      "Children": [
        {
          "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
          "Text": "\r\nWe need to create the sensitivity analysis framework now. We try adding as a new experiment in same APSIM-X file (see below, we separate if becomes messy) that:\r\n\r\nimage\r\n\r\nDetails:\r\n\r\n1- Run fodder-beet/catch-crop rotations from 1971 to 2000\r\n\r\n2- Four locations/.met already added here: K:\\Rainshelter\\MultiCropRotation_APSIM_X\\ObservedData\\Weather\\SensAnMet\r\n\r\nimage\r\n\r\n3- Management\r\n\r\nSow automatically FB on 15 Nov\r\nHarvest FB on 15 May\r\nSow CC on 15 June\r\nHarvest CC on 10 Nov\r\n4- Factorial treatments:\r\n\r\n2 x water (rain-fed x fully irrigated)\r\n2 x N (0 or 400 kg N/ha on fodder beet)\r\n5- Important aspects\r\n\r\nContinuous rotation (no soil re-set) for 30 years",
          "Name": "Experiment Description",
          "Children": [],
          "IncludeInDocumentation": true,
          "Enabled": true,
          "ReadOnly": false
        },
